attributes.background:
Illegal immigrants, prisoners and juvenille delinquents should be given the "opportunity" to do something useful in the community. 

There are plenty of "opportunities" in the community, such as:

1. Sorting through household waste and retrieving items that can be recycled;

2. Clean the streets of litter;

3. Clean the sewers;

4. Recycle our own electronic equipment, instead of sending it to poor countries like China;

5. Clean the waterways (rivers, canals and coastlines);
